It might be a whole new year, but some challenges remain the same. For the first seven days of 2023, the Nelspruit SPCA has already had 99 animals surrendered to it – and it needs your help to feed them. “If you can help us by donating food for dogs, cats, puppies and kittens it will really help us a lot,” the society recently asked. ALSO READ: Valencia robbers arrested, one remains on the run “We can’t do this without your support.” In the same breath, the SPCA thanked the community for having assisted them thus far, especially for the kind donations during the festive season.